"publications/OpenWPM_1_million_site_tracking_measurement.pdf)"

#: ../content/posts/fpdetection.md:block 10 (unordered list)
msgid ""
"[The Web Never "
"Forgets](https://securehomes.esat.kuleuven.be/~gacar/persistent/the_web_never_forgets.pdf)"
msgstr ""
"[[Веб никогда не забывает](https://securehomes.esat.kuleuven.be/~gacar/"
"persistent/the_web_never_forgets.pdf)"

#: ../content/posts/fpdetection.md:block 10 (unordered list)
msgid "We reflected traits of known fingerprinting tools like:"
msgstr "Мы отразили черты известных инструментов дактилоскопии, таких как:"

#: ../content/posts/fpdetection.md:block 10 (unordered list)
#, fuzzy
msgid "[FingerprintJS](https://github.com/fingerprintjs)"
msgstr "[FingerprintJS](https://github.com/fingerprintjs)"

